# Colorizr Gem

## Overview
This gem allows the user to color strings with the following colors:
  red
  green
  yellow
  blue
  pink
  light_blue
  white
  light_grey
  black

New colors can easily be added by changing the self.available_colors method.


## Usage
Using the gem is very simple, simply call the method by the color's name like here:
  "A STRING".red
or
  a_string= "THIS IS A STRING";
  a_string.blue;


## Installation instructions
To install, simply download the gem and use the following command:
  gem install colorizr-[version].gem
  ie: gem install colorizr-0.0.1.gem

Do not forget to add the following to your code:
  require 'colorizr'


Enjoy the gem!
